WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
narrator: replay walks the HMAC-chained audit log plus the receipts.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
narrator: the same data in JSONL — ready to pipe into jq or splunk.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:22.000
narrator: verify recomputes every HMAC and checks receipt monotonicity.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.000
narrator: a zero exit code is what a healthcheck cron pins to.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:33.900
narrator: any tamper would fail verify and surface here.
